  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/631af354d89eea15e268f8cc45564349.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=72 /></span>On a quest to restore your weary body in the mountains of Japan, you nearly perish and arrive at the steps of Maison Chichigami. There, you earn the favor of Chichigami Manami and her daughters, who hire you as a live-in tutor. Heal your body and soul living a life of luxury in the company of absolute goddesses! Fall in love with the matronly Manami, the playful Rio, the bookish Kana, and the diligent Ai! But watch your step as you explore the mansion. The Chichigami lineage is steeped in history, and dark secrets may be lying in wait...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/0af92aea9b3c9d4f3b71b7ff61a2d144.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=73 /></span>Search the vast estate of Maison Chichigami! Wander about the mansion over the course of a week and socialize with the mansion's various residents. Watch the story unfold before your very eyes!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/8beaeb4c659ca5dbff943c4358bf3157.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/7e3f54769518c7a647285196e3df4684.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/f1f82375000ccdc1abb368a5f9c2b11b.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/e85c75e51883b3b33f6798a26eb43258.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/3ef6d57c47701d40ece63ff5e492416e.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/4f2f7325e4d9e1c662ef2103c080b97e.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gorgeous animation!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gawk at the beautiful residents of Maison Chichigami and their highly animated expressions! Get up close and personal and (respectfully) appreciate their massive charms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience the Story!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse your way to the ending by experiencing the story through immersive narration. Each character has a unique personality that brings the story to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/631af354d89eea15e268f8cc45564349.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=72 /></span>On a quest to restore your weary body in the mountains of Japan, you nearly perish and arrive at the steps of Maison Chichigami. There, you earn the favor of Chichigami Manami and her daughters, who hire you as a live-in tutor. Heal your body and soul living a life of luxury in the company of absolute goddesses! Fall in love with the matronly Manami, the playful Rio, the bookish Kana, and the diligent Ai! But watch your step as you explore the mansion. The Chichigami lineage is steeped in history, and dark secrets may be lying in wait...<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/0af92aea9b3c9d4f3b71b7ff61a2d144.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=73 /></span>Search the vast estate of Maison Chichigami! Wander about the mansion over the course of a week and socialize with the mansion's various residents. Watch the story unfold before your very eyes!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/8beaeb4c659ca5dbff943c4358bf3157.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/7e3f54769518c7a647285196e3df4684.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/f1f82375000ccdc1abb368a5f9c2b11b.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/e85c75e51883b3b33f6798a26eb43258.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/3ef6d57c47701d40ece63ff5e492416e.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2914480/extras/4f2f7325e4d9e1c662ef2103c080b97e.avif?t=1749388789\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gorgeous animation!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gawk at the beautiful residents of Maison Chichigami and their highly animated expressions! Get up close and personal and (respectfully) appreciate their massive charms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience the Story!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse your way to the ending by experiencing the story through immersive narration. Each character has a unique personality that brings the story to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
